Line25.FBCF5: You did good. Be smarter than she was. Alright?
Line23.FBCF5: As for Bakira... (long sigh) She needs a burial. I’ll see it done. And the Sisterhood should know of the coin. Let them figure out what to do with it.
Line21.FBCF5: You and me, we’re done here. You saw masters in action. Bested one, even. I can’t teach you better than that.
